[[Trash collection]] in the small [[Sicilian]] town of Castelbuono is now done by donkeys rather thank trucks. This [[low tech]] solution not only replaces the [[fossil fuel]] consumption and [[diesel fumes]] (see [[air pollution]]) of the trucks, but they are less expensive. The donkeys collect the rubbish in sacks.


